      "Detail": {
        "de": {
          "Title": "Al Plan Dolomites Hotel Museum",
          "Header": null,
          "BaseText": "<p>Wanduhren, Schnitzereien, Masken, Flaschenst&ouml;psel, Korkenzieher, Pfeifen, Kaffeem&uuml;hlen und K&uuml;chenger&auml;te, religi&ouml;se Gegenst&auml;nde,&nbsp;Oldtimer und Motorr&auml;der, etwa mehrere Vespas,&nbsp;z&auml;hlen zur privaten Sammlung der Familie Trebo. Die Objekte erz&auml;hlen Geschichten aus den letzten 150 Jahren und sind auf die unterschiedlichen R&auml;ume des Hotels verteilt.</p>",
          "Keywords": null,
          "Language": "de",
          "MetaDesc": "Alle Informationen zu aktuellen Ausstellungen • Öffnungszeiten • Kontakt • Preise. Al Plan Dolomites Hotel Museum freut sich auf Ihr Kommen!",
          "AuthorTip": null,
          "IntroText": "",
          "MetaTitle": "Al Plan Dolomites Hotel Museum • Museen in Südtirol",
          "SubHeader": null,
          "SafetyInfo": null,
          "ParkingInfo": null,
          "GetThereText": null,
          "EquipmentInfo": null,
          "AdditionalText": null,
          "PublicTransportationInfo": null
        },
        "en": {
          "Title": "Al Plan Dolomites Hotel Museum",
          "Header": null,
          "BaseText": "<p>Wall clocks, carvings, masks, bottle stoppers, corkscrews, pipes, coffee grinders and kitchen equipment, religious objects, antique cars and motorcycles, such as several Vespas, are part of the Trebo family&rsquo;s private collection. The objects tell stories from the last 150 years and are distributed across different rooms of the hotel.</p>",
          "Keywords": null,
          "Language": "en",
          "MetaDesc": "All information about • current exhibitions • opening times • contact and • pricing! Al Plan Dolomites Hotel Museum is looking forward to your visit.",
          "AuthorTip": null,
          "IntroText": null,
          "MetaTitle": "Al Plan Dolomites Hotel Museum • Museums in South Tyrol",
          "SubHeader": null,
          "SafetyInfo": null,
          "ParkingInfo": null,
          "GetThereText": null,
          "EquipmentInfo": null,
          "AdditionalText": null,
          "PublicTransportationInfo": null
        },
        "it": {
          "Title": "Al Plan Dolomites Hotel Museo",
          "Header": null,
          "BaseText": "<p>Orologi a muro, opere in legno intagliato, maschere, tappi di bottiglia, cavatappi, pipe, macinini per il caff&egrave; e utensili da cucina, oggetti religiosi, oldtimer e motociclette, come diversi modelli di Vespa: fanno parte della collezione della famiglia Trebo. Raccontano storie anche di 150 anni fa e sono disseminati nei diversi locali dell&rsquo;hotel.</p>",
          "Keywords": null,
          "Language": "it",
          "MetaDesc": "Tutte le informazioni su • mostre e eventi artistici • orari d'apertura • contatti e • prezzi. Archeoparc Velturno vi aspetta!",
          "AuthorTip": null,
